# @version ^0.2.16
# contracts/Factory.vy

struct ContractEndProposal:
        employer_status: int128
        employee_status: int128
        init_time: uint256

from . import Employment

#interface Employment():
#    def setup(_employer:address, _employee: address, _contract_value: uint256, _severance_percent: decimal, _period: uint256, _grace: uint256): payable

#NewEmployment: event({token: indexed(address), exchange: indexed(address)})


MAX_CONTRACTS: constant(int128) = 128
PLATFROM_FEE_PERCENT: constant(uint256) = 1

employmentTemplate: public(address)

employer_contracts: public(HashMap[address, address[MAX_CONTRACTS]])
employer_contract_count: public(HashMap[address, int128])

employee_contracts: public(HashMap[address, address[MAX_CONTRACTS]]) 
employee_contract_count: public(HashMap[address, int128])

employer_employees: public(HashMap[address, HashMap[address, bool]])

@external
def initializeFactory(template: address):
    assert self.employmentTemplate == ZERO_ADDRESS
    assert template != ZERO_ADDRESS
    self.employmentTemplate = template

@external
@payable
def createEmployment(employee: address, contract_value: uint256, severance_percent: uint256, period: uint256, grace: uint256) -> address:
    assert self.employmentTemplate != ZERO_ADDRESS
    assert self.employer_employees[msg.sender][employee] == False
    assert self.employee_contract_count[employee] < MAX_CONTRACTS
    assert self.employer_contract_count[msg.sender] < MAX_CONTRACTS
    assert contract_value == msg.value
    assert severance_percent >= 0 and severance_percent+PLATFROM_FEE_PERCENT <= 100
    assert period > 0
    
    employment_contract: address = create_forwarder_to(self.employmentTemplate)
    employer: address = msg.sender

    Employment(employment_contract).setup(employer, employee, contract_value, severance_percent, period, grace, value=contract_value)

    employer_contract_current: int128 = self.employer_contract_count[employer]
    self.employer_contracts[employer][employer_contract_current] = employment_contract
    self.employer_contract_count[employer] = self.employer_contract_count[employer] + 1

    employee_contract_current: int128 = self.employee_contract_count[employee] 
    self.employee_contracts[employee][employee_contract_current] = employment_contract
    self.employee_contract_count[employee] = self.employee_contract_count[employee] + 1

    self.employer_employees[employer][employee] = True

    #log.NewExchange(token, exchange)
    return employment_contract


@external
@view
def getEmploymentsWithEmployee(employee: address) -> address[MAX_CONTRACTS]:
    return self.employee_contracts[employee]

@external
@view
def getNumEmploymentsPerEmployee(employee: address) -> int128:
    return self.employee_contract_count[employee]

@external
@view
def getEmploymentsWithEmployer(employer: address) -> address[MAX_CONTRACTS]:
    return self.employer_contracts[employer]

@external
@view
def getNumEmploymentsPerEmployer(employer: address) -> int128:
    return self.employer_contract_count[employer]
